{"tid":1412623,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"等效光圈一問？！","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:54:21.000Z","uid":299063,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8ceddced09ba824f145412091518db0c538ac342","tid":1412623,"uid":299063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"我知全片幅鏡頭, 放係apsc機身，等效焦距同等效光圈都要x1.5。<br />\n但係... 請問！🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n！！！sony A7iii 開apsc模式，！！！！用全片幅鏡頭，<br />\n假設50mm f/1.8，<br />\n等效焦距會係75mm啦，咁等效光圈會有影響嗎？係維持F1.8，定係要x1.5？"},{"pid":"d2aa063a8106442d08112fb347b01aaa50a1a142","tid":1412623,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"乘返1.5"},{"pid":"62433bded70996f8b5f45d61d3056d82396bc30b","tid":1412623,"uid":26080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"入光量不變<br />\n景深你會係EVF 睇到"},{"pid":"71f47ffb3c345db205ad723129315db5d8a4cfae","tid":1412623,"uid":299063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d2aa063a8106442d08112fb347b01aaa50a1a142","tid":1412623,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"乘返1.5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思... 想問深入啲，<br />\nA7iii就算係開咗apsc模式，但佢個感光元件依然係全片幅啊，<br />\n咁以我理解，sony只需要全片幅size嘅畫面截取成apsc嘅size，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3r7mE4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3r7mE4.png&h=fe793d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解會影響光圈？"},{"pid":"bfe789a08d9e5ef081c75d5f0995a39d7fd8ad24","tid":1412623,"uid":50972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"入光量係一樣<br />\n其實個所謂等效景深咪即係又係50 1.8個景深"},{"pid":"1a816d30b0c6850d3f64bc1aaccf776b6b26e6ce","tid":1412623,"uid":258598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46542e69761bf9bc7db85b82c76b35ef5d5f05a8","tid":1412623,"uid":43668,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"apsc mode同apsc機都係crop左4邊 <br />\n即係同你ff mode影完crop左佢係一樣<br />\n假設50 1.8 影一樣既構圖 你ff企1米 apsc要企1.4米(假設) 咁個景深咪唔同 ff近被攝體所以淺d景深<br />\n但如果你ff企1.4米 之後crop返做apsc構圖 其實係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a607c46f8572a489e4ab21ded9201ad341d49219","tid":1412623,"uid":57,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71f47ffb3c345db205ad723129315db5d8a4cfae","tid":1412623,"uid":299063,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d2aa063a8106442d08112fb347b01aaa50a1a142","tid":1412623,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"乘返1.5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思... 想問深入啲，<br />\nA7iii就算係開咗apsc模式，但佢個感光元件依然係全片幅啊，<br />\n咁以我理解，sony只需要全片幅size嘅畫面截取成apsc嘅size，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3r7mE4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3r7mE4.png&h=fe793d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解會影響光圈？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"淨係景深有影響, 支鏡光圈係1.8就係1.8"},{"pid":"0e6559ea25c2c95686929ab76c2a99dcd11cb4c2","tid":1412623,"uid":10152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"景深有影響 通光量冇影響"},{"pid":"2bd9b3023dcd8c945c947c35a8099fdc2e5db72d","tid":1412623,"uid":252756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ceddced09ba824f145412091518db0c538ac342","tid":1412623,"uid":299063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"我知全片幅鏡頭, 放係apsc機身，等效焦距同等效光圈都要x1.5。<br />\n但係... 請問！🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n！！！sony A7iii 開apsc模式，！！！！用全片幅鏡頭，<br />\n假設50mm f/1.8，<br />\n等效焦距會係75mm啦，咁等效光圈會有影響嗎？係維持F1.8，定係要x1.5？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"等效焦距x1.5係方便計買咩焦段鏡頭<br />\n等效光圈x1.5/1.4係方便計買幾大光圈影人像<br />\n<br />\n例如sigma 18-35 f1.8 art<br />\nF1.8 x 1.5 = F2.7<br />\n咁sigma呢支apsc鏡即係屬於28-52 f2.8大三元鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n雖然光圈決定光斑有幾大<br />\n但其實鏡頭結構會大大影響散景質素<br />\n而散景質素係層次感嘅重點<br />\n所以追散景除左光圈仲要睇sample photo<br />\n<br />\n而聲稱等效光圈影響相片質素/曝光能力之類嘅<br />\n純粹係J緊自己部機個高iso應力<br />\n唔使理嗰啲人士"},{"pid":"ed1acc4119fc51937a554015a5cd6ff92d170306","tid":1412623,"uid":252756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://dofsimulator.net/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdofsimulator.net%2Fen%2F&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=e9688bbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dofsimulator.net/en/</a><br />\n自己試"},{"pid":"099be55d048d49db3e7e0ea157e6220ba79ea4e5","tid":1412623,"uid":75900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:47:05.000Z","msg":"直接當支50 1.8係apsc鏡就係"},{"pid":"0d6e769fc0f9b2064a7b944dd2f9797166fabfa0","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"咁apsc 機身+鏡既F2.8<br />\n其實係咪同ff機+ff鏡既景深同入光量一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f815d18381dcbb08a73ae125447bb7965c74fdb","tid":1412623,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0d6e769fc0f9b2064a7b944dd2f9797166fabfa0","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"咁apsc 機身+鏡既F2.8<br />\n其實係咪同ff機+ff鏡既景深同入光量一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:50:10.000Z","msg":"景深會冇咁淺 入光係一樣<br />\n<br />\n其實係咁嘅 大光圈呢 啲散景越邊越散嘅 咁apsc就係crop走左ff條邊嘛 所以就望落冇咁散"},{"pid":"5d4298843c47f488c995fff5124005eb52162c6c","tid":1412623,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:00:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a08e0b365e26da3e6794da24a634a774d6ec7b74","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f815d18381dcbb08a73ae125447bb7965c74fdb","tid":1412623,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0d6e769fc0f9b2064a7b944dd2f9797166fabfa0","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"咁apsc 機身+鏡既F2.8<br />\n其實係咪同ff機+ff鏡既景深同入光量一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:50:10.000Z","msg":"景深會冇咁淺 入光係一樣<br />\n<br />\n其實係咁嘅 大光圈呢 啲散景越邊越散嘅 咁apsc就係crop走左ff條邊嘛 所以就望落冇咁散"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁apsc鏡既50-140 f2.8用落apsc機度<br />\n景深就等同ff機ff鏡既70200 f4<br />\n係咪咁理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44119f95778e92cfed9f284ecf20ba76e55047d2","tid":1412623,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a08e0b365e26da3e6794da24a634a774d6ec7b74","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f815d18381dcbb08a73ae125447bb7965c74fdb","tid":1412623,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0d6e769fc0f9b2064a7b944dd2f9797166fabfa0","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"咁apsc 機身+鏡既F2.8<br />\n其實係咪同ff機+ff鏡既景深同入光量一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:50:10.000Z","msg":"景深會冇咁淺 入光係一樣<br />\n<br />\n其實係咁嘅 大光圈呢 啲散景越邊越散嘅 咁apsc就係crop走左ff條邊嘛 所以就望落冇咁散"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁apsc鏡既50-140 f2.8用落apsc機度<br />\n景深就等同ff機ff鏡既70200 f4<br />\n係咪咁理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"冇咁簡單 不過類近"},{"pid":"858f97cd0039fbce406825a02ad93d44c7f6d8a1","tid":1412623,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"入光量一樣<br />\n構圖一樣的話因你要行遠少少影, 所以散景效果大慨係X 1.5<br />\n50 1.8 大約 = FF 2.8左右<br />\n<br />\n如果相同距離就係1.8"},{"pid":"a5b32a350479043faae02c288886acf0cf6ab698","tid":1412623,"uid":255414,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"我嘅理解係咁<br />\n唔計等效光圈<br />\napsc用16 1.4影出嚟=24 1.4<br />\nff用24 1.4影出嚟=24 1.4<br />\n因為鏡頭焦距大D，所以ff影出嚟嘅散景D。<br />\n是咪咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e0042684f5ac1a3fc1ab744f9070e4605256ca","tid":1412623,"uid":191921,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"46542e69761bf9bc7db85b82c76b35ef5d5f05a8","tid":1412623,"uid":43668,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"apsc mode同apsc機都係crop左4邊 <br />\n即係同你ff mode影完crop左佢係一樣<br />\n假設50 1.8 影一樣既構圖 你ff企1米 apsc要企1.4米(假設) 咁個景深咪唔同 ff近被攝體所以淺d景深<br />\n但如果你ff企1.4米 之後crop返做apsc構圖 其實係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"簡單講，光圈同距離一樣個陣。。<br />\napsc 景深較深，但快門可以快d ... 就係咁。。。<br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記t 值。。。。有時標個光圈係大。。。t 值就縮哂水"},{"pid":"810d7a85d46aac3f7f1ee02722f986dd82914756","tid":1412623,"uid":10152,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a5b32a350479043faae02c288886acf0cf6ab698","tid":1412623,"uid":255414,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"我嘅理解係咁<br />\n唔計等效光圈<br />\napsc用16 1.4影出嚟=24 1.4<br />\nff用24 1.4影出嚟=24 1.4<br />\n因為鏡頭焦距大D，所以ff影出嚟嘅散景D。<br />\n是咪咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"景深其中一個因素係要睇個光圈直徑<br />\n<br />\nF/1.4 果個F 係指Focal Length <br />\n<br />\n所以 85mm f/1.8 比起 35mm f/1.8 既景深更淺 即使大家都係 f/1.8 前者大約47 後者大約20<br />\n<br />\n去翻你問題 你apsc既 16mm f/1.4 雖然有24mm 視角（因為crop左） 但你支 16mm既光圈直徑 係 16mm/1.4 大約11.5 所以去到24mm 大約係 f/2.1"},{"pid":"7ec64c2b95b058478d622cbd99b07a00582f10e9","tid":1412623,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"唔識個d..試下<br />\ncrop 一張35.4 相到50mm<br />\n係咪=50.4咁散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee13930b86e46ac4b8f429738f22488e6669e1f8","tid":1412623,"uid":10152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"810d7a85d46aac3f7f1ee02722f986dd82914756","tid":1412623,"uid":10152,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a5b32a350479043faae02c288886acf0cf6ab698","tid":1412623,"uid":255414,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"我嘅理解係咁<br />\n唔計等效光圈<br />\napsc用16 1.4影出嚟=24 1.4<br />\nff用24 1.4影出嚟=24 1.4<br />\n因為鏡頭焦距大D，所以ff影出嚟嘅散景D。<br />\n是咪咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:11:07.000Z","msg":"景深其中一個因素係要睇個光圈直徑<br />\n<br />\nF/1.4 果個F 係指Focal Length <br />\n<br />\n所以 85mm f/1.8 比起 35mm f/1.8 既景深更淺 即使大家都係 f/1.8 前者大約47 後者大約20<br />\n<br />\n去翻你問題 你apsc既 16mm f/1.4 雖然有24mm 視角（因為crop左） 但你支 16mm既光圈直徑 係 16mm/1.4 大約11.5 所以去到24mm 大約係 f/2.1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"以上計法 所以啲人成日都會話 xf50-140 f/2.8<br />\n<br />\n大約 = FF 70-210 f/4<br />\n<br />\n支 xf56 f/1.2 大約等同 FF 85mm f/1.8<br />\n<br />\n全部都係上面條式出黎 （景深）<br />\n<br />\n但強調翻 通光量係一樣"},{"pid":"1c60f85c35860a7ddedf1f77538efb057db22ec7","tid":1412623,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcf2859fa09e2b07c59714dbd3b2e96f069ea13d","tid":1412623,"uid":11116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a08e0b365e26da3e6794da24a634a774d6ec7b74","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f815d18381dcbb08a73ae125447bb7965c74fdb","tid":1412623,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0d6e769fc0f9b2064a7b944dd2f9797166fabfa0","tid":1412623,"uid":43662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"咁apsc 機身+鏡既F2.8<br />\n其實係咪同ff機+ff鏡既景深同入光量一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":